{{unreferenced|date=January 2017}}
'''Mangnejo''' ({{lang-sd|منڱڻيجو}}) is a [[Sindhi names|Sindhi tribe]] in [[Sindh]], [[Pakistan]]. Mangneja tribe is settled in [[Kamber Shahdadkot District]] [[Khairpur District|Khairpur]], [[Karachi]], [[Sukkur District|Sukkur]], [[Naushahro Feroze District|Naushahro Feroze]], [[Tando Allahyar District|Tando Allahyar]], [[Hyderabad District, Pakistan|Hyderabad]] and [[Larkana District|Larkano]] [[districts of Sindh]].

The Mangneja speak the [[Sindhi language]].

